<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>skeptict - GitHub Pages</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        .container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: left;
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 90%;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        
        .main-content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 2%;
        }

        .links, .weblog, .other-links {
            width: 32%;
        }

        .links ul, .other-links ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .links li, .other-links li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .links a, .other-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #667eea;
        }

        .links a:hover, .other-links a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            background: none;
            -webkit-background-clip: unset;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: unset;
            background-clip: unset;
        }

        .post {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .post h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .post .date {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #888;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .highlight {
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #a8edea 0%, #fed6e3 100%);
            padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .footer {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            padding-top: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.2);
            color: #888;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .main-content {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .links, .weblog, .other-links {
                width: 100%;
                margin-bottom: 2rem;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>skeptict</h1>
        <div class="main-content">
            <div class="links">
                <h2>Daily Reading</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="https://www.economist.com" target="_blank">The Economist</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://www.theatlantic.com" target="_blank">The Atlantic</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://www.nytimes.com" target="_blank">The New York Times</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="weblog">
                <h2>Weblog</h2>
                <div class="post">
                    <h3>First Post</h3>
                    <p class="date">October 28, 2025</p>
                    <p>This is my first weblog post. I'm excited to share my thoughts with you.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="other-links">
                <h2>Links</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#" target="_blank">Link 1</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" target="_blank">Link 2</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" target="_blank">Link 3</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Built with ❤️ on GitHub Pages</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
